page.title: 19What we saw at the stream
page.content: {Wildlife:}Cabbage White butterfly, Gate keeper butterfly, Peacock butterfly, Blue Wing dragonfly, Green-veined White butterfly, green wing dragonfly, plovers, kingfishers, swifts, heron, water vole and minnows. {Trees:}Grey alder, hawthorn, elder, pollarded willows, silver birch, field maple, sloe and ash. {Plants:}Reed canary grass, burdock, great willow herb, great chickweed, skullcap, common persicaria, dock, comfrey, woody nightshade, goose grass, spear thistle, corn sowthistle, common hemp nettle, hedge parsley, brooklime, bindweed, tufted vetch, cut-leaved cranesbill, red campion, meadowsweet, and reedmace bulrush.
